            "text": "<h3>Standard / 3-5 Business Days / Estimated price of $15.00</h3><p>We offer reliable standard shipping with delivery within 3 to 5 business days. </p><h3>Pick-Up In Store / 3-5 Business Days / Free</h3><p>Choose our free in-store pick-up option and collect your order at a location near you within 3 to 5 business days.</p><h3>Express Home / 1-2 Business Days / Estimated price of $15.00</h3><p>For those who need their items quickly, our express home delivery ensures your order arrives within 1 to 2 days.</p>",
            "text_2": "<h3>Exchange & Returns</h3><h3>Free Store Return</h3><p>You can return your items to any of our stores as long as the return is made in the same market where you made the purchase. Returns are always free of charge, and the deadline for returns is 30 days from the delivery confirmation date.</p><h3>Free Home Return</h3><p>Request a home return easily through your account. We offer free home returns, and you have 30 days from the delivery confirmation date to send back your items.</p>",
